{
  "chapter": "085",
  "title": "吕不韦列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦其人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳翟</span>的大商人。他往来各地，贱价买入、高价卖出，家中积累了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>的财富。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "安国君立为太子",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>了。到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十二年</span>，立次<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>有一个特别宠爱的姬妾，立她为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">正夫人</span>，号称<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>嗣。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>的中子名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏姬</span>，不受宠爱。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>作为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">质子</span>被派往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国屡次<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>打<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>也不太礼遇。"
    },
    "2.2": {
      "title": "奇货可居",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">庶孽</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">孙</span>，在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>那里当人质，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘</span>用度不宽裕，居处困顿，不得意。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>做生意，见到他很怜悯，说：\"这是<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">奇货可居</span>啊。\""
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦游说子楚",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>前去见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>，说：\"我能光大您的门庭。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>笑着说：\"你姑且光大自己的门庭，再来光大我的门庭吧！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>说：\"您不知道啊，我的门庭要等您的门庭光大了才能光大。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>心里明白他说的意思，就请他坐下，深入交谈。"
    },
    "3.2": {
      "title": "吕不韦献策",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王年老了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>被立为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。我私下听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>宠爱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>嗣，能决定嫡嗣人选的只有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>而已。现在您<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀人</span>，您又居于中间，不怎么受宠，长期在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>那里做人质。一旦大王<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>继位为王，那么您就没有希望与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长子</span>以及早晚侍奉在跟前的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸子</span>争夺<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之位了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>说：\"是这样。怎么办呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>说：\"您贫穷，在这里作客，没有什么可以奉献给亲长和结交<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>的。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>虽然贫穷，请允许我拿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>为您西行游说，侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>，立您为嫡嗣。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>就叩头说：\"如果真能按您的策略行事，请让我分<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国与您共享。\""
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "4.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦西游秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>就拿出<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五百金</span>给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>，作为日常用度和结交<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>的费用；又用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五百金</span>购买奇物珍玩，亲自带着西行游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国，求见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">姊</span>姐，把这些物品全都献给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>。顺便盛赞<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>贤能智慧，结交了遍布<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>宾客，常说\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：子楚\">楚（子楚）</span>把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>当作天，日夜哭泣思念<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>\"。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>大为欢喜。"
    },
    "4.2": {
      "title": "游说华阳夫人",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>于是让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">姊</span>姐劝说<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>：\"我听说，凭姿色侍奉人的，姿色衰退爱情就会减退。现在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，非常受宠却没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>嗣，不趁此时早早从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸子</span>中选择贤孝的人，立为嫡嗣，认作自己的儿子，丈夫在世时就会受到敬重，丈夫<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>之后，所认的儿子继位为王，终身不会失势，这就是所谓一句话而得<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">万世（时长）</span>之利啊。不在年轻貌美时树立根基，等到姿色衰退、爱情消减之后，即使想说一句话，还能办到吗？现在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>贤能，而他自知是中子，按次序不能成为嫡嗣，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲又不受宠，自己来依附<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>如果确实在此时提拔他为嫡嗣，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>就终身在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国有依靠了。\""
    },
    "4.3": {
      "title": "约立子楚为嫡嗣",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>觉得有理，趁<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>空闲时，从容地说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国做人质非常贤能，来往的人都称赞他。于是哭着说：\"我有幸得以充实后宫，不幸没有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>嗣，希望立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>为嫡嗣，以托付妾身。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>答应了，就与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>刻了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉符</span>，约定立<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>为嫡嗣。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>因此厚赠<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>，并请<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>做他的老师，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>因此在<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>中名声更盛。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "5.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦献姬生政",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>娶了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>姿色绝佳、善于跳舞的姬妾同居，知道她已怀孕。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>跟着<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>饮酒，看到这位姬妾后很喜欢，就起身为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>祝寿，请求赐予这位姬妾。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>生气，心念自己已经<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>费家产为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>，想借此钓取奇货，就献出了这位姬妾。姬妾隐瞒已经怀孕的事实，到满了足月之时，生下了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">政（秦始皇）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>于是立这位姬妾为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "6.1": {
      "title": "子楚脱归秦",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五十年</span>，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王齮</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>攻<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，形势危急，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>密谋，用<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">六百斤</span>黄金贿赂看守的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>，得以逃脱，逃奔到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>军，于是得以归国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国豪门的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>儿，得以藏匿，因此<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母子</span>二人都得以活命。"
    },
    "6.2": {
      "title": "昭王薨，子楚为太子",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">秦昭王</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五十六年</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">安国君（秦孝文王）</span>继位为王，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳夫人（华阳太后）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">王后</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国也把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">政（秦始皇）</span>送回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "7.1": {
      "title": "孝文王崩，庄襄王立",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">孝文王（秦孝文王）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>继位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span>的养<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳（华阳太后）</span>后被尊为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">华阳太后</span>，亲<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏姬</span>被尊为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏太后</span>。"
    },
    "7.2": {
      "title": "吕不韦为丞相",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元年</span>，任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，封为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文信侯</span>，把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万户</span>作为<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">食</span>邑。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "8.1": {
      "title": "始皇立，吕不韦为相国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span>即位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">政（秦始皇）</span>继位为王，尊<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，号称\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">仲父</span>\"。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王年少，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>时时暗中与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>私通。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>的家僮有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万人</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "9.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦招致士人",
      "text": "当时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏无忌\">信陵君（魏无忌）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">春申君</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">平原君</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">孟尝君</span>，都礼遇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，喜好<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>以互相倾轧争胜。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>凭借<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国的强大，以不如他们为耻，也招致<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>人，厚待他们，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">食客</span>多至<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span>。"
    },
    "9.2": {
      "title": "著吕氏春秋",
      "text": "这时<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>中有很多<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>，如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">荀卿</span>之流，著书遍布<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>就让他的门客人人写下自己所见所闻，汇集整理成<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">八览</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">六论</span>、<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">十二纪</span>，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀万言</span>。自认为囊括了<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">天地</span>万物古今之事，取名为<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">吕氏春秋</span>。将它张贴在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>市门，在上面悬挂<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>，招请<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">游士</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span>中有能增删一字的赏<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "10.1": {
      "title": "进嫪毐入宫",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇帝（秦始皇）</span>渐渐长大，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>的淫乱不止。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>担心事发祸及自己，就私下寻找阳物硕大的人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>作为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，时常放纵歌舞伎乐，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：嫪毐\">毐（嫪毐）</span>用他的阳物贯穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">桐轮</span>行走，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>听说此事，以此引诱<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>听说后，果然想私下得到他。"
    },
    "10.2": {
      "title": "诈腐为宦者",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>于是进献<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>，假意让人以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">腐罪</span>举报他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>又暗中对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>说：\"可以假装施行腐刑，这样他就能供事宫中。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>就暗中厚赠主掌腐刑的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">吏</span>，假意判他的罪，拔掉他的胡须眉毛作为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宦者</span>，于是得以侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>私下与他通奸，极为宠爱。怀了身孕，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>怕别人知道，诈称占卜需要避时，迁宫居于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>常常随从，赏赐极为丰厚，事情都由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>决断。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>的家僮<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千人</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸客</span>求官为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千馀人</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "11.1": {
      "title": "夏太后薨",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏太后</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">孝文王（秦孝文王）</span>的后叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">华阳太后</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦孝文王\">孝文王（秦孝文王）</span>合葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">寿陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏太后</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span>葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">芷阳</span>，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏太后</span>独自葬在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杜</span>东，说：\"东望我的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，西望我的丈夫。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百年（时长）</span>之后，旁边应当有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万家邑</span>。\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "12.1": {
      "title": "嫪毐事发",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，有人告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>其实不是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宦者</span>，经常与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>私乱，生了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，都藏匿起来。与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>谋划说：\"大王一旦<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝，就以我的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>为继承人。\"于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王交付官吏审讯，尽得实情，事情牵连到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>。"
    },
    "12.2": {
      "title": "夷嫪毐三族",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九月</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">夷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>三<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>所生的两个<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>，把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">迁</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>家产全部被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">没</span>收，并被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">迁</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地。秦王想<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span>，因为他奉事<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先王</span>功劳大，加上为他<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">游说</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">辩士</span>很多，秦王不忍心绳之以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "13.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦免相",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十年十月</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">免</span>去了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">相国</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>的职务。等到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">茅焦</span>劝说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王才把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>迎回<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">咸阳</span>，而让<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文信侯</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>的封国。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": ""
    },
    "14.1": {
      "title": "吕不韦饮鸩而死",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宾客</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">使者</span>络绎不绝于道，去拜访<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文信侯</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王担心他变乱，就赐给<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文信侯</span>一封<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">书</span>信说：\"你对<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国有什么功劳？<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国封你于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>，食<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万户</span>。你与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>国有什么亲戚关系？号称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">仲父</span>。你与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">家属</span>搬迁到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>去吧！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>自度渐渐受到逼迫，恐怕被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀，就饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酖</span>酒而<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王所加怒的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>都已死去，于是让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">迁</span>到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地的人都复归回来。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "太后薨",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦始皇\">始皇（秦始皇）</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十九年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">薨</span>逝，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太后</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">庄襄王（秦庄襄王）</span>合葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">茝阳</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>尊贵显赫，封号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">文信侯</span>。有人告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">嫪毐</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：嫪毐\">毐（嫪毐）</span>听说了。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>王询问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">左右</span>，没有立刻发作。秦王到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍郊</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：嫪毐\">毐（嫪毐）</span>恐祸起，就与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">党</span>羽谋划，矫用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玺</span>发兵<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲年宫</span>。秦王派吏<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：嫪毐\">毐（嫪毐）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：嫪毐\">毐（嫪毐）</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>逃亡，被追上后<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">好畤</span>，于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了他的宗族。而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕不韦</span>由此被罢黜。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>所说的\"闻\"（徒有虚名）的人，大概就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">吕（吕不韦）</span>这类人吧？"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "太史公赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吕不韦\">不韦（吕不韦）</span>钓取奇货，以身质托付<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：秦庄襄王\">子楚（秦庄襄王）</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：华阳太后\">华阳（华阳太后）</span>册立嗣子，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>献上美<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>。 等到受封<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河南</span>，竟号称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">仲父</span>。 被迁<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>以惩其谤议，悬挂千金以求增减一字。 筹策已经成功，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">富贵</span>就此<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>得。"
    }
  }
}